org.dockbox.selene.proxy.annotations

Annotation Type Instance


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface Instance
    The annotation used to mark a parameter as instance provider for methods annotated with Proxy.Target. Parameters with this annotation are excluded from the target method lookup, and are automatically injected.
